short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Open any link on Side Panel

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Expand your Side Panel experience to boost up productivity and multitasking with our extension. “Link to Side Panel” changes the browsing game for advanced users and ordinary enjoyers of Google. 
Explore any link through the Side Panel for effective browsing without limitations. More importantly, enjoy our multiple windows feature to open different links on the Side Panel simultaneously. Adjust your multiple Side Panel windows to your linking to enhance your browser’s capacity to the fullest. 
Our Link to Side Panel will help you organise information, save time, and make your browsing life easier!

Who are we?
NoName Technology is a young and ambitious team, working on optimising users’ browser experience. Our Link to Side Panel doesn't show ads and doesn't send users' data anywhere.
